{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"w5ej8rx5rn7c37yul52sm87","title":"1129 Nand2tetris","desc":"","updated":1670250677174,"created":1669691084582,"custom":{},"fname":"0drops.2022.1129-nand2tetris","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"c4357b18f86138a88d5d12e1f6d7e8f3","links":[],"anchors":{"前言":{"type":"header","text":"前言","value":"前言","line":8,"column":0,"depth":2},"網路公開課-build-a-modern-computer-from-first-principles":{"type":"header","text":"網路公開課 Build a Modern Computer from First Principles","value":"網路公開課-build-a-modern-computer-from-first-principles","line":34,"column":0,"depth":3},"nand2tetris-網站":{"type":"header","text":"Nand2tetris 網站","value":"nand2tetris-網站","line":45,"column":0,"depth":3},"我的筆記":{"type":"header","text":"我的筆記","value":"我的筆記","line":51,"column":0,"depth":2},"x-and-y":{"type":"header","text":"(x AND y)","value":"x-and-y","line":53,"column":0,"depth":3},"x-or-y":{"type":"header","text":"(x OR y)","value":"x-or-y","line":57,"column":0,"depth":3},"notx":{"type":"header","text":"NOT(x)","value":"notx","line":61,"column":0,"depth":3},"commutative-laws":{"type":"header","text":"Commutative Laws","value":"commutative-laws","line":65,"column":0,"depth":3},"associative-laws":{"type":"header","text":"Associative Laws","value":"associative-laws","line":70,"column":0,"depth":3},"distributive-laws":{"type":"header","text":"Distributive Laws","value":"distributive-laws","line":75,"column":0,"depth":3},"de-morgan-laws":{"type":"header","text":"De Morgan Laws","value":"de-morgan-laws","line":80,"column":0,"depth":3},"用來簡化看來很複雜的邏輯":{"type":"header","text":"用來簡化看來很複雜的邏輯","value":"用來簡化看來很複雜的邏輯","line":85,"column":0,"depth":3},"邏輯表":{"type":"header","text":"邏輯表","value":"邏輯表","line":89,"column":0,"depth":3},"小結":{"type":"header","text":"小結","value":"小結","line":103,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"0YMTMineOCu8QrkzCD9rn","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"1129-nand2tetris\">1129 Nand2tetris<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#1129-nand2tetris\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"前言\">前言<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#前言\"></a></h2>\n<p>真的很想知道記憶體超頻那些數字到底是在調什麼... 第三章 Memory 有提到記憶體的運作方式，來看看能不能開竅...</p>\n<p>絕對要配這個看:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://programmermagazine.github.io/mag/ymag201506/book.html\">Nand2Tetris 慕課記 -- 從邏輯閘到方塊遊戲 by 陳鍾誠老師</a></p>\n<p>課程章節:</p>\n<pre><code>0. From Nand to Tetris\n1. Boolean Functions\n2. Boolean Arithmetic\n3. Memory\n4. Machine Language\n5. Computer Architecture\n6. Assembler\n7. VM I: Stack Arithmetic\n8. VM II: Program Control\n9. High-Level Language Project\n10. Compiler I: Syntax Analysis Project\n11. Compiler II: Code Generation Project\n12. Operating System\n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"網路公開課-build-a-modern-computer-from-first-principles\">網路公開課 Build a Modern Computer from First Principles<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#網路公開課-build-a-modern-computer-from-first-principles\"></a></h3>\n<p>就是這兩堂課:</p>\n<p><img src=\"/assets/images/2022-11-29-11-32-17.png\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>[Build a Modern Computer from First Principles: From Nand to Tetris (Project-Centered Course) by Shimon Schocken, Noam Nisan](<a href=\"https://www.coursera\">https://www.coursera</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>.org/learn/build-a-computer)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.coursera.org/learn/nand2tetris2\">Build a Modern Computer from First Principles: Nand to Tetris Part II (project-centered course) by Shimon Schocken</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"nand2tetris-網站\"><a href=\"http://nand2tetris.org/\">Nand2tetris 網站</a><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#nand2tetris-網站\"></a></h3>\n<p><img src=\"/assets/images/2022-11-29-11-37-00.png\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>可以前往下載講義/簡報/習題</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"我的筆記\">我的筆記<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#我的筆記\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"x-and-y\">(x AND y)<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#x-and-y\"></a></h3>\n<p>x∧y</p>\n<h3 id=\"x-or-y\">(x OR y)<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#x-or-y\"></a></h3>\n<p>x∨y</p>\n<h3 id=\"notx\">NOT(x)<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#notx\"></a></h3>\n<p>¬x</p>\n<h3 id=\"commutative-laws\">Commutative Laws<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#commutative-laws\"></a></h3>\n<p>(x AND y) = (y AND x)<br>\n(x OR y) = (y OR x)</p>\n<h3 id=\"associative-laws\">Associative Laws<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#associative-laws\"></a></h3>\n<p>(x AND (y AND z)) = ((x AND y) AND z))\n(x OR (y OR z)) = ((x OR y) OR z))</p>\n<h3 id=\"distributive-laws\">Distributive Laws<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#distributive-laws\"></a></h3>\n<p>(x AND (y OR z)) = (x AND y) OR (x AND z)\n(x OR (y AND z)) = (x OR y) AND (x OR z)</p>\n<h3 id=\"de-morgan-laws\">De Morgan Laws<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#de-morgan-laws\"></a></h3>\n<p>NOT(x AND y) = NOT(x) OR NOT(y)\nNOT(x OR y) = NOT(x) AND NOT(y)</p>\n<h3 id=\"用來簡化看來很複雜的邏輯\">用來簡化看來很複雜的邏輯<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#用來簡化看來很複雜的邏輯\"></a></h3>\n<p><img src=\"/assets/images/2022-12-05-22-19-29.png\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"邏輯表\">邏輯表<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#邏輯表\"></a></h3>\n<p>總共有這幾種可能</p>\n<p><img src=\"/assets/images/2022-12-05-22-21-29.png\"></p>\n<p>其實遇到邏輯複雜的我都只是表列後一一寫下 QQ</p>\n<p>簡化真的要另外花時間，感覺以後可以請 ChatGPT 幫我看一下能不能簡化。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/assets/images/2022-12-05-22-30-24.png\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://programmermagazine.github.io/mag/ymag201506/book.html#nand2tetris-%E7%AC%AC-1-%E9%80%B1----%E5%B8%83%E6%9E%97%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B8\">NAND 元件具有全能性，也就是其它邏輯閘都可以由一群 NAND 所組合而成</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"小結\">小結<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#小結\"></a></h2>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","